text: Mahmoud Balah (born 5 August 1942) is a Syrian wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman 78 kg at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1942 births Category:Living people Category:Syrian male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Syria Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
